MediaItems.Comment: 4 electric car charging stations facing the road - TYPE 2 connection - near the main entrance of the Longarone Exhibition Center at the foot of the Dolomites, available 24 hours a day on the route for Cadore - Cortina - Comelico - Auronzo - Misurina. 4 parking spaces available for parking electric cars for recharging even during the Longarone Fiere Dolomiti trade fairs such as Arredamont, MIG - International Exhibition of Artisan Gelato, Ri-Costruire 3.0, Agrimont, Forest Fair & Festival, Expo Dolomiti HoReCa, etc. ...
